duction/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161430/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-15.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-15/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161430/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-15-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eForget plug-in tunes; Joe has tweaked this engine the old-fashioned way. A ported and polished cylinder head improves airflow to the 0.4mm over-bored cylinders fitted with Mahle pistons, while valve timing is managed by Piper performance camshafts.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161435/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-16.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161435/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-16-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-16\" data-attachment-id=\"653137\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161435/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-16.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-16/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161435/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-16-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe intake features individual throttle bodies with 3D-printed upswept trumpets fed by a ram-air intake on the bonnet. A skimmed head and block increase the compression while the whole setup is controlled by a standalone MicroSquirt ECU.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161442/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-18-680x453.jpg\" a