oduction/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161416/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-11-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eA Supersprint manifold and custom exhaust produce great noise, while a 5-speed gearbox from a later Panda makes the most out of the powerband. And how much power? Don’t let the badges fool you – this little beast packs 115 horses in its little stable.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161621/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-43.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161621/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-43-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-43\" data-attachment-id=\"653164\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161621/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-43.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-43/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161621/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-43-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161625/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-44-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-44\" data-attachment-id=\"653165\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161625/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-44.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-44/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161625/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-44-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161412/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-10-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-10\" data-attachment-id=\"653131\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161412/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-10.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-10/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161412/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-10-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eOutside, as much as it betrays its roots, Joe’s Panda looks every bit the part. Up front, a functional chassis-mounted splitter and air dam designed by Joe are complemented by side skirts and a wing atop the tailgate. Don’t underestimate homemade aero parts; \u003ca title=\"The Pinderwagen: This Is What Peak Performance Looks Like\" href=\"http://www.speedhunters.com/2023/08/pinderwagen-peak-performance-looks-like/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eyou’d be surprised at what they can achieve\u003c/a\u003e…\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161408/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-9.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161408/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-9-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-9\" data-attachment-id=\"653130\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161408/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-9.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-9/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161408/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-9-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161342/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-3-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-3\" data-attachment-id=\"653124\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161342/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-3.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-3/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161342/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-3-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161404/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-8-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-8\" data-attachment-id=\"653129\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161404/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-8.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-8/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161404/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-8-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eBeneath the rolled and pulled wheel arches are 14-inch Oscam split rims wrapped in Nankang NS2-R tyres for the road, with a separate set of ATIWE Borbets for track days. Other unique touches include 3D-printed blanks replacing the original door mirrors, now swapped for a single ‘overtaking’ mirror.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161423/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-13.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161423/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-13-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-13\" data-attachment-id=\"653134\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161423/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-13.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-13/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161423/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-13-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor design symmetry, a left-hand drive taillight has replaced the reverse light, and in an attempt to shed weight, Joe crafted custom polycarbonate windows, complete with a slider for the driver’s door.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161347/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-4.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161347/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-4-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-4\" data-attachment-id=\"653125\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161347/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-4.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-4/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161347/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-4-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eBehind the wheels is a ‘big’ brake kit featuring later model 240mm discs paired with Wilwood callipers and a brake bias valve. Thanks to bespoke LEDA coilovers with Mk1 Ford Fiesta top mounts, Joe has achieved a 180mm drop.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161541/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-33.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161541/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-33-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-33\" data-attachment-id=\"653154\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161541/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-33.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-33/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161541/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-33-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eInside, despite being stripped out, the Panda is surprisingly pleasant. After all, it was designed to be minimal, so it was almost made to be exposed.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161553/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-36.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161553/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-36-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-36\" data-attachment-id=\"653157\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161553/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-36.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-36/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161553/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-36-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161604/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-39-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-39\" data-attachment-id=\"653160\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161604/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-39.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-39/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161604/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-39-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161545/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-34-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-34\" data-attachment-id=\"653155\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161545/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-34.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-34/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161545/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-34-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eA full FIA-spec roll cage safeguards the occupants, custom-fabricated by ARC Autosport, who also crafted the mounts for the Recaro Pole Position driver’s seat and Cobra classic passenger bucket. TAKATA Racing harnesses secure both sides.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161617/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-42.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161617/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-42-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-42\" data-attachment-id=\"653163\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161617/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-42.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-42/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161617/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-42-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161537/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-32-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-32\" data-attachment-id=\"653153\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161537/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-32.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-32/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161537/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-32-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161600/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-38-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-38\" data-attachment-id=\"653159\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161600/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-38.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-38/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161600/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-38-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eAs with the exterior, the details make the Panda’s interior stand out. A full respray in pastel grey elevates the cabin, courtesy of Jack Smith, aka Forged From Flake. I have no shame in shouting Jack out – his work is phenomenal.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161609/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-40.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161609/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-40-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-40\" data-attachment-id=\"653161\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161609/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-40.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-40/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161609/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-40-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161549/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-35-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-35\" data-attachment-id=\"653156\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161549/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-35.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-35/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161549/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-35-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161521/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-28-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-28\" data-attachment-id=\"653149\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161521/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-28.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-28/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161521/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-28-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161506/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-24.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161506/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-24-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-24\" data-attachment-id=\"653145\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161506/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-24.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-24/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161506/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-24-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eMy favourite details include the rare Abarth steering wheel, which rivals the leather bar tape on the door bars for quirkiness, and the 3D-printed gauge binnacle designed to attach to the roll bar – space is at a premium in this little car.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161502/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-23.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161502/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-23-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-23\" data-attachment-id=\"653144\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161502/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-23.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-23/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161502/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-23-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161518/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-27-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-27\" data-attachment-id=\"653148\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161518/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-27.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-27/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161518/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-27-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161514/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-26-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-26\" data-attachment-id=\"653147\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161514/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-26.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-26/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161514/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-26-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161529/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-30-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-30\" data-attachment-id=\"653151\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161529/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-30.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-30/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161529/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-30-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eA pedal box conversion and tower short shifter complete the interior, finished off with a custom-turned wooden shift knob.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161525/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-29.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161525/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-29-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-29\" data-attachment-id=\"653150\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161525/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-29.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-29/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161525/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-29-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eBut why go through such effort building an Italian econobox like this? In Joe’s words: \u003cem\u003e“I built it the way I did because I’ve had track cars in the past and love the driving as much as the building. I didn’t want to build a show car and get overly protective over it.”\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161455/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-21.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161455/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-21-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-21\" data-attachment-id=\"653142\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161455/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-21.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-21/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161455/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-21-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003e“I also thought it would be funny to chase people down in a little white box on a track day. Imagine the Panda in your mirrors; you’d have a right giggle!\u003c/em\u003e” And therein lies the innocence of Joe’s Fiat, something missing from so many modified cars nowadays.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161458/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-22.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161458/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-22-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"MC White Goods Panda SH-22\" data-attachment-id=\"653143\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161458/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-22.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/10/big-fun-in-little-italy-a-mighty-mk1-fiat-panda/mc-white-goods-panda-sh-22/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08161458/MC-White-Goods-Panda-SH-22-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe Panda straddles the line between not taking itself too seriously and taking the execution of the build as seriously as possible.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhat a fantastic little car – the fastest washing machine this side of a laundromat.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMario Christou\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\nInstagram: \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mcwpn\" target=\"_blank\"\u003emcwpn\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mariochristou.world\" target=\"_blank\"\u003emariochristou.world\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://mariochristou.world/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003emariochristou.world\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
